<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Gdata_Spreadsheets_DocumentQuery and Zend_Gdata_Spreadsheets_ListQuery do not require Zend_Gdata_App_Exception before throwing said exception. As a result, if any errors are encountered a class not found exception is thrown instead of something more informative.</p>

<p>Unit tests also need to be added to these classes (and CellQuery) to make sure that failure cases are handled appropriately.</p>

